{"tid":2375571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"我造成大家困擾了！染疫影響旁人 日本1女子疑為此自殺身亡","createTime":"2021-01-22T06:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T07:05:33.000Z","uid":75969,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"2b3153ec7d00aaa678d3debdb293b45c585605d1","tid":2375571,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"日本放送協會（NHK）報導，相關人士表示一名30多歲的女性，本月被發現死於東京都住處內。死者生前確診染疫後就在自家療養；從現場狀況來看，這名女性應是尋短。<br />\n<br />\n現場留有一張紙條，上面寫著「很抱歉因為我造成身旁人士的困擾」。<br />\n<br />\n據指出，女性死者染疫後雖然幾乎沒有症狀，但女性身旁的人都因此擔心「我有可能被傳染」。相關單位將調查詳細案情。<br />\n<br />\n日本早稻田大學副教授上田路子說，很多人染疫後不光會擔心自己的身體健康，也可能憂慮會不會傳染給家人，甚至可能受到社會嚴厲譴責，因此在精神上必須承受各種不同的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5194821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F5194821&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=f318fab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5194821</a>"},{"pid":"059486b06eb1b03603fdecf444f3436fc95e2675","tid":2375571,"uid":237459,"like":9,"dislike":13,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"日本人係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2c86d52acc07f20c255352edf158cb36344875","tid":2375571,"uid":156144,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:42:46.000Z","msg":"CLS文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc054ba664bcc2aa6d049dcd4235033fbfc63f36","tid":2375571,"uid":156440,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"主要係日本垃圾社區文化<br />\n<br />\n如果傳染咗比人 令到對方沒有工作 等於間接性禍害左人哋家庭幸福<br />\n<br />\n自己有病亦都會俾人話自己唔檢點 日日出入門口俾人篤眼篤鼻<br />\n<br />\n日本個垃圾文化就係咁樣